snippet.title: Evil Spirits Do Exist - Game Teaser
snippet.description:
Game Teaser - The Prophecy

Play the ESDE game. It is a new kind of online horror game with a unique real world gameplay. It's a game about the many faces of evil that exist all around us and we choose to ignore every day.

Site: http://www.evilspiritsdoexist.com/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EvilSpiritsGame

Find me : 
https://twitter.com/Ninaki_Limpi
https://www.instagram.com/katerinalimp/
https://www.facebook.com/katerinalimpi

Video by https://www.youtube.com/user/troxelcassie 
Thank you for warning us all!!
